(32, 'Laptop Apple MacBook Air 2017 i5', 'laptop-apple-macbook-air-2017-i5', 123, 18890000, '1607076931apple-macbook-air-mqd32sa-a-i5.jpg', 'Phụ kiện: sạc, cáp, tai nghe', 12, 'mới 100%', 'Khuyến mại: Dán màn hình', 1, '<div class=\"characteristics\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, Freesans, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, Freesans, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none; zoom: 1;\">Đặc điểm nổi bật của Apple MacBook Air 2017 i5 1.8GHz/8GB/128GB (MQD32SA/A)</h2><div id=\"owl-detail\" class=\"owl-carousel owl-detail owl-theme\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; width: 652.594px; overflow: hidden; top: 1px; opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"owl-wrapper-outer autoHeight\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; width: 652.594px; transition: height 500ms ease-in-out 0s; height: 363px;\"><div class=\"owl-wrapper\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); backface-visibility: hidden; width: 10448px; left: 0px; transition: all 0ms ease 0s;\"><div class=\"owl-item\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; backface-visibility: hidden; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); width: 653px;\"><div class=\"item\" data-id=\"86282\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"><img class=\"lazyOwl\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/106875/Slider/vi-vn-macbook-air-2017.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; width: 652.992px; height: auto;\"></div></div><d