; max-height: 584px;\"></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, Freesans, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Có thể gắn thẻ nhớ vào adapter để sử dụng cho thiết bị (<a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Laptop chính hãng, giá tốt, bán tại Thế Giới Di Động\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(80, 168, 227); outline: none; zoom: 1;\">laptop</a>,&nbsp;macbook, máy ảnh)&nbsp;có hỗ trợ khe cắm thẻ SD</strong></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: 0px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\">Lưu ý: đối với thẻ Transcend bạn cần kiểm tra độ tương thích thiết bị&nbsp;<a href=\"https://vn.transcend-info.com/Support/compatibility/product/423/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Kiểm tra tương thích thẻ nhớ\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(80, 168, 227);\">tại đây</a>&nbsp;trước khi chọn mua.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: 0px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\"><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-3-1.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(80, 168, 227);\"><img alt=\"Thẻ nhớ MicroSD 128 GB Class 10 sử dụng được với nhiều thiểt bị\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-3-1.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" title=\"Thẻ nhớ MicroSD 128 GB Class 10 sử dụng được với nhiều thiểt bị\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-3-1.jpg\" style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 584px;\"></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, Freesans, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\"><b style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Dung lượng 128 GB giúp tăng bộ nhớ máy</b></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: 0px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\"><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-4-fix.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(80, 168, 227);\"><img alt=\"Thẻ nhớ MicroSD 128 GB Class 10 lữu trữ hơn 40.000 bài hát\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-4-fix.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" title=\"Thẻ nhớ MicroSD 128 GB Class 10 lữu trữ hơn 40.000 bài hát\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-4-fix.jpg\" style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 584px;\"></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, Freesans, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Class 10 biểu thị cho tốc độ của thẻ nhớ</strong></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: 0px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\">Tương tự như dung lượng RAM trên điện thoại càng cao - máy càng nhanh, thì con số 10 hiển thị cho việc tốc độ ghi của thẻ sẽ nhanh hơn so với class 2, 4 và 6 trên thị trường hiện nay.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: 0px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\"><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-5-1.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(80, 168, 227);\"><img alt=\"Thẻ nhớ MicroSD 128 GB Class 10 chuẩn class 10\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-5-1.jpg\" class=\"lazy\" title=\"Thẻ nhớ MicroSD 128 GB Class 10 chuẩn class 10\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-5-1.jpg\" style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 584px;\"></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, &quot;DejaVu Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, Freesans, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tốc độ đọc, ghi chép dữ liệu nhanh</strong></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: 0px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\">* Tốc độ đọc dữ liệu là&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">45 MB/s</strong>: mở xem 1 video nặng&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1 GB&nbsp;chưa tới&nbsp;30 giây</strong>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: 0px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\">* Tốc độ ghi dữ liệu&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">10 MB/s</strong>: chép một video dung lượng&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1 GB</strong>&nbsp;vào thẻ nhớ<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;chưa tới&nbsp;2 phút</strong>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; margin-block-start: 0px; margin-block-end: 0px; text-rendering: geometricprecision;\"><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-docghi.gif\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(80, 168, 227);\"><img alt=\"Thẻ nhớ Micro SD 128 GB Class 10 - Tốc độ đọc, ghi dữ liệu nhanh\" data-original=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-docghi.gif\" class=\"lazy\" title=\"Thẻ nhớ Micro SD 128 GB Class 10 - Tốc độ đọc, ghi dữ liệu nhanh\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/55/71046/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1-docghi.gif\" style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 584px;\"></a></p><div class=\"boxRtAtc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"likewied\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"likeshare\" style=\"margin: 10px 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; float: left; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"fb-like fb_iframe_widget\" data-href=\"/the-nho-dien-thoai/the-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-action=\"like\" data-size=\"small\" data-show-faces=\"false\" data-share=\"true\" fb-xfbml-state=\"rendered\" fb-iframe-plugin-query=\"action=like&amp;app_id=242045172499368&amp;container_width=0&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegioididong.com%2Fthe-nho-dien-thoai%2Fthe-nho-microsd-128gb-class-10-uhs1&amp;layout=button_count&amp;locale=vi_VN&amp;sdk=joey&amp;share=true&amp;show_faces=false&amp;size=small\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; float: right; display: inline-block; position: relative; text-align: justify; verti